#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:82
msgid "输入产品名称。下方为系统支持的检测项列表，可按需启用/关闭。"
msgstr ""
"Enter a product name. Below is the list of inspection items the system "
"supports, which you can enable or disable as needed."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品第二步"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:88
msgid "**将 PCB 放在传送带上**"
msgstr "**Place the PCB on the Conveyor**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:90
msgid ""
"将 PCB 平整放置于传送带中央，选择对应传送带并点击“锁定”。输入或确认传送带宽度参数，随后点击“进板”，PCB "
"将自动输送至相机下方的拍摄/定位区域；到位后点击“下一步”。"
msgstr ""
"Place the PCB flat in the center of the conveyor, select the corresponding "
"conveyor, and click \"Lock\". Enter or confirm the conveyor width "
"parameter, then click \"PCB In\"; the PCB is automatically conveyed to the "
"capture/positioning area beneath the camera. Once in place, click \"Next\"."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst
msgid "将PCB放在传送带上示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:96
msgid "**输入 PCB 尺寸**"
msgstr "**Enter PCB Dimensions**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:98
msgid ""
"若已知 PCB 尺寸，直接输入其宽度与高度（单位：mm），然后点击“下一步”。 若尺寸不确定，可移动相机分别拍摄 PCB "
"左下角与右上角，在图像上依次点击这两个位置并选择 **自动计算** ，系统将自动推算尺寸。"
msgstr ""
"If the PCB dimensions are known, enter the width and height directly (in "
"mm), then click \"Next\". If the dimensions are uncertain, move the camera "
"to capture the lower-left and upper-right corners of the PCB, click these "
"two positions on the image in turn, and choose **Auto Calculate**; the "
"system will automatically estimate the dimensions."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst
msgid "自动尺寸计算示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:105
msgid "**完整 PCB 拍摄**"
msgstr "**Capture Full PCB**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:107
msgid ""
"点击“拍摄”，系统将联动相机与传送带分区采集并自动拼接生成完整 PCB 图像。 "
"随后点击“定义区域”，在图像上框选用于自动编程的有效区域（通常为整板；若需排除治具/夹具边缘，可适当收缩）。 "
"该基准图像将作为后续自动编程、对齐与检测的参考，务必使用洁净、无缺陷的 **Golden board（良品板）** 拍摄。 "
"此界面可实时调整相机参数（亮度、曝光、增益、白平衡、点云滤波等）；如效果不佳，可重新拍摄覆盖上一版本。"
msgstr ""
"Click \"Capture\"; the system coordinates the camera and conveyor to "
"capture the board in sections and automatically stitches them into a "
"complete PCB image. Then click \"Define Area\" and frame the valid region "
"used for auto-programming (usually the whole board; shrink it slightly to "
"exclude fixture/jig edges if needed). This reference image serves as the "
"baseline for subsequent auto-programming, alignment, and inspection, so be "
"sure to capture it from a clean, defect-free **Golden board**. Camera "
"parameters (brightness, exposure, gain, white balance, point-cloud "
"filtering, etc.) can be adjusted in real time on this screen; if the result "
"is poor, recapture to overwrite the previous version."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst
msgid "完整 PCB 拍摄"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:116
msgid "**半自动编程（上传 CAD）**"
msgstr "**Semi-Automatic Programming (Upload CAD)**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:118
msgid ""
"提供 CAD（.csv）文件后，系统可： - 自动读取：封装(Package)、丝印/标识、料号(PN)、X/Y 坐标、旋转角度； - "
"按封装或料号聚类，同类元件一次建模，加速训练； - 减少后续人工分组与命名工作。"
msgstr ""
"After you provide a CAD (.csv) file, the system can: - automatically read "
"Package, silkscreen/designator, Part Number (PN), X/Y coordinates, and "
"rotation angle; - cluster components by package or part number so identical "
"components are modeled once, accelerating training; - reduce subsequent "
"manual grouping and naming work."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:123
msgid "若不提供 CAD，后续自动编程仍可执行；检测质量不受影响，仅失去基于封装/料号的聚类加速，系统将对元件逐一建模。"
msgstr ""
"If no CAD is provided, auto-programming can still run; inspection quality is "
"unaffected — only the package/part-number clustering acceleration is lost, "
"and the system models each component individually."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "上传 CAD 文件界面"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:129
msgid ""
"步骤： 1. 上传 `.csv` 文件并点击“预览表格”。 2. "
"在字段映射界面依次指定：料号(PN)、封装(Package)、X、Y、旋转(°)，（可选）层/板面字段；如存在多层数据，可按层号或面别过滤。 3."
" 选择坐标单位（mm 或 mil），确认原点与方向一致。 4. 点击“运行自动编程”。"
msgstr ""
"Steps: 1. Upload the `.csv` file and click \"Preview Table\". 2. In the "
"field-mapping screen, assign in order: Part Number (PN), Package, X, Y, "
"Rotation (°), and (optionally) layer/side fields; if multi-layer data "
"exists, you can filter by layer number or side. 3. Select the coordinate "
"unit (mm or mil) and confirm the origin and orientation are consistent. 4. "
"Click \"Run Auto Programming\"."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "字段映射示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:139
msgid ""
"若 CAD "
"初次与拍摄图像未正确重合，系统将进入“对齐调整”界面；通过旋转、平移、缩放（必要时辅助少量基准点）微调至主要元件位置大致重合后，点击“重新运行自动编程”即可重新生成。"
msgstr ""
"If the CAD does not initially align correctly with the captured image, the "
"system opens the \"Alignment Adjustment\" screen; use rotation, "
"translation, and scaling (with a few reference points if needed) to fine-"
"tune until the main components roughly coincide, then click \"Rerun Auto "
"Programming\" to regenerate."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:141
