msgstr "**Auto Programming (No CAD)**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:143
msgid "不上传任何文件，直接点击“自动编程”即可。系统会通过视觉+AI自动："
msgstr ""
"Without uploading any file, simply click \"Auto Programming\". Using vision "
"plus AI, the system automatically:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:145
