#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:146
msgid "推断类别特征并生成初始检测模板；"
msgstr "infers category features and generates initial inspection templates;"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:147
msgid "建立后续对齐与检测所需的结构化数据。"
msgstr "builds the structured data required for subsequent alignment and inspection."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:149
msgid "自动编程耗时约 30 秒。"
msgstr "Auto-programming takes about 30 seconds."

