#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:166
msgid ""
"点击“+ 标记”，框选 PCB "
"上固定的参考标记（圆形、矩形或复杂图案均可）。框选区域应略大，以保证在轻微位移情况下仍能正确定位。确认后，点击“预测中心”完成标记定义。"
msgstr ""
"Click \"+ Mark\" and frame a fixed reference mark on the PCB (circular, "
"rectangular, or a complex pattern all work). Frame a slightly larger region "
"so positioning still succeeds under minor displacement. After confirming, "
"click \"Predict Center\" to finish defining the mark."

