#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:174
msgid ""
"左侧显示自动编程获得的元件列表。若上传了 CAD，系统会自动显示丝印/标识，并将同类元件分组。 "
"可通过搜索栏过滤存在问题的项。对于标记不正确的元件，可手动删除并重新编程。"
msgstr ""
"The left panel lists the components obtained from auto-programming. If a CAD "
"was uploaded, the system automatically shows silkscreen/designators and "
"groups identical components. Use the search bar to filter problematic "
"items. For incorrectly marked components, you can manually delete and "
"reprogram them."

