msgstr ""
"After confirming that all component boxes and attributes are correct, click "
"\"Train\" to start model training (about 1 minute)."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst
msgid "训练示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:192
msgid "训练完成后，点击“自动生成检测参数”，系统会基于当前模板与训练结果生成一套初始检测参数。"
msgstr ""
"When training completes, click \"Generate Inspection Parameters\"; the "
"system generates an initial set of inspection parameters based on the "
"current templates and training results."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:194
msgid "随后点击“评估全部”，系统将批量评估所有元件，并以颜色标记（绿：健康；红：不健康）。可按需查看不健康项并参考 :ref:`检测参数` 继续微调。"
msgstr ""
"Then click \"Evaluate All\"; the system evaluates every component in batch "
"and marks them by color (green: healthy; red: unhealthy). Review the "
"unhealthy items as needed and fine-tune them by referring to the Inspection "
"Parameters section."

